        <body>
            <div>
               
	<pb facs="liv_001195_0001" n="0001"/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><space extent="1" unit="words"/><placeName>Manchester</placeName> <add place="inline"><hi rend="red" hand="#U">6</hi></add>
<lb/><space extent="1" unit="words"/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/><date when="1858-01-28">28th January
<lb/><space extent="1" unit="words"/><space extent="3" unit="chars"/>1858</date></p>
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">My Dear Sir</p><!-- Change line info as appropriate -->
<lb/><p>Your salary
<lb/>will commence
<lb/>on the <date when="1858-02-01">1<hi rend="sup underline">st</hi> February</date>
<lb/>and should you
<lb/>want more than
<lb/>a quarter's advance</p><!-- could be "quarter's advance, but would need second opinion. #BL-->
<lb/>
<lb/><cb rend="vertical"/><ab>I shall be in <placeName><settlement type="city">London</settlement></placeName> on <date when="1858-01-30">Saturday</date></ab>

	<pb facs="liv_001195_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">I shall feel obliged
<lb/>if you let me
<lb/>know - <choice><sic>Dont</sic><corr>Don't</corr></choice>
<lb/>leave your
<lb/>friends in any
<lb/>hurry on account
<lb/>of that. If you 
<lb/>can get your
<lb/>things better
<lb/>where you are
<lb/>than in <placeName><settlement type="city">London</settlement></placeName>

	<pb facs="liv_001195_0003" n="0003"/>
<lb/>by all means do so -
<lb/>and you can 
<lb/>remit the money
<lb/>afterwards - We
<lb/>must get all 
<lb/>into <unclear cert="low">trim</unclear> by 
<lb/>the <date when="1858-02-15">15<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi></date></p>
<lb/><p>Anything that
<lb/>I can get for 
<lb/>you please let 
<lb/>me know

	<pb facs="liv_001195_0004" n="0004"/>
<lb/>and if possible
<lb/>I shall do my
<lb/>best to comply
<lb/>with your
<lb/>wishes - the
<lb/>amount of luggage
<lb/>has to be limited
<lb/>but we shall try
<lb/>and make each 
<lb/>other as comfortable
<lb/>as possible.</p>
<lb/><closer><salute>I am &amp;c</salute> <signed><persName>David Livingstone</persName></signed></closer><!-- End of name on page 1 --> 

<!--page breaks not showing up correctly--><!--Pagebreaks seem fine to me. #BL-->

